Chen Yuntao is begging on the streets of Hefei City to raise money for his son Chen Minghao . 
  The nine-year-old is suffering from leukaemia and has had 20 courses of chemotherapy . 
  Father is dressed as a horse and begging for five yuan – the equivalent of 54p – for a ride . 
  The family are already in huge debt after spending £21,800 on his cancer treatment . 
 